content: I've been listening to "My Favorite Murder" for over a year now, and I'm always looking for new true crime podcasts to listen to. I think I'll check out "Crime Junkie" and "Last Podcast on the Left" first, since they sound like they have a similar tone to "My Favorite Murder". By the way, I've been really into TV shows lately, and I just realized I've been watching a lot of Netflix originals. Do you think I can get a list of all the Netflix original shows that have been released this year?
